      <title>Markdown&amp;&amp;Latex语法学习</title>
      <link href="/2019/02/09/Markdown-Latex%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/"/>
      <url>/2019/02/09/Markdown-Latex%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>工欲善其事，必先利其器。对于经常需要写各种科技论文（英文/中文）以及技术博客的童鞋而言，掌握常用的<code>MarkDown、Latex</code>语法尤为重要。这篇博客讲述一些最频繁使用的<code>MarkDown、Latex</code>语法以及自身所填的一些坑。<br><a id="more"></a></p><h1 id="从Word走来"><a href="#从Word走来" class="headerlink" title="从Word走来"></a>从Word走来</h1><p>我们最开始接触的排版软件是微软出品的Office,它是一个足够强大的软件，但当涉及大量的数学公式、图表的编号和交叉引用时，Office内置的丑陋公式字体和薄弱的交叉应用功能就显得苍白无力了。<br>但大部分学校的本科毕业论文好像并不支持Latex, 所以还是有必要扯一下Office。</p><h2 id="word"><a href="#word" class="headerlink" title="word"></a>word</h2><p>对于word而言，<a href="http://www.mathtype.cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>MathType</strong></a>是支持最好的公式编辑软件，但是MathType是收费的，而且价格昂贵。这里提供一个<a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/1VgBaxxgDUq1RAkqw5Y-2iQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener">下载链接</a>, 提取码是:<code>7xin</code>。安装好并破解就可以永久使用了。 </p><h2 id="ppt"><a href="#ppt" class="headerlink" title="ppt"></a>ppt</h2><p>对于ppt而言，有一个比较好的开源插件支持Latex语法的使用:<a href="http://www.jonathanleroux.org/software/iguanatex/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>IguanaTex</strong></a>。它会调用Latex编译器来编译Latex代码并生成无损的图片(意味着不必担心放大十倍而模糊)甚至矢量图。它支持所有的Latex语法，所以我们可以用这个插件键入代码生成数学公式、流程图等并以ppt的形式展示。<br><img src="//hfutzzw.github.io/2019/02/09/Markdown-Latex语法学习/slide1.PNG" alt="公式"><br><img src="//hfutzzw.github.io/2019/02/09/Markdown-Latex语法学习/slide2.PNG" alt="流程图"></p><h1 id="走到Web端去"><a href="#走到Web端去" class="headerlink" title="走到Web端去"></a>走到Web端去</h1><p>在本地书写markdown语言并渲染成html是写技术博客的常用做法。<br>书写markdown语言推荐使用<a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>VScode</strong></a>及其提供的MarkDown在本地实时预览的插件：<strong>Markdown Preview Enhanced</strong>。顺带说一下，开源的VScode真是神器，它在<a href="https://github.com/Microsoft/vscode" target="_blank" rel="noopener">github</a>上的star非常高。</p><h2 id="Markdown语法"><a href="#Markdown语法" class="headerlink" title="Markdown语法"></a>Markdown语法</h2><p>markdown的语法非常简单，我们只需掌握经常使用的十几个语法即可，大家自行查看。</p><h3 id="代码块"><a href="#代码块" class="headerlink" title="代码块"></a>代码块</h3><p><code>import tensorflow as tf</code><br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">from __future__ import absolute_import</span><br><span class="line">from __future__ import print_function</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">from torch.utils.data import DataLoader</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">from .dataset_loader import ImageDataset, VideoDataset</span><br><span class="line">from .datasets import init_imgreid_dataset, init_vidreid_dataset</span><br><span class="line">from .transforms import build_transforms</span><br><span class="line">from .samplers import build_train_sampler</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">class BaseDataManager(object):</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    @property</span><br><span class="line">    def num_train_pids(self):</span><br><span class="line">        return self._num_train_pids</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    @property</span><br><span class="line">    def num_train_cams(self):</span><br><span class="line">        return self._num_train_cams</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    def return_dataloaders(self):</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">        Return trainloader and testloader dictionary</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">        return self.trainloader, self.testloader_dict</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    def return_testdataset_by_name(self, name):</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">        Return query and gallery, each containing a list of (img_path, pid, camid).</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">        return self.testdataset_dict[name][&apos;query&apos;], self.testdataset_dict[name][&apos;gallery&apos;]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h3 id="插入本地-网络图片、超链接"><a href="#插入本地-网络图片、超链接" class="headerlink" title="插入本地/网络图片、超链接"></a>插入本地/网络图片、超链接</h3><ul><li><p>超链接<br><a href="https://www.baidu.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">百度</a></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[超链接名](超链接地址)</span><br><span class="line">[百度](https://www.baidu.com/)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>插入本地/网络图片<br><img src="http://www.hfut.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/69/b1/245c5de846fd96fa699eb5a39501/554bd2c9-13f5-4fd2-a53c-d2263184963f.jpg" alt="新年"></p></li></ul><p><img src="http://www.hfut.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/69/b1/245c5de846fd96fa699eb5a39501/554bd2c9-13f5-4fd2-a53c-d2263184963f.jpg" width="500" height="150" align="center"><br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![图片名](图片地址)</span><br><span class="line">![新年](http://www.hfut.edu.cn/_upload/article/images/69/b1/245c5de846fd96fa699eb5a39501/554bd2c9-13f5-4fd2-a53c-d2263184963f.jpg)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><center class="half">    <img src="https://image.baidu.com/search/detail?ct=503316480&z=0&ipn=d&word=gakki&step_word=&hs=0&pn=9&spn=0&di=78416382440&pi=0&rn=1&tn=baiduimagedetail&is=0%2C0&istype=0&ie=utf-8&oe=utf-8&in=&cl=2&lm=-1&st=undefined&cs=4122311673%2C3141545856&os=224815105%2C2698122340&simid=0%2C0&adpicid=0&lpn=0&ln=1862&fr=&fmq=1549686406169_R&fm=&ic=undefined&s=undefined&hd=undefined&latest=undefined&copyright=undefined&se=&sme=&tab=0&width=undefined&height=undefined&face=undefined&ist=&jit=&cg=&bdtype=0&oriquery=&objurl=http%3A%2F%2F06imgmini.eastday.com%2Fmobile%2F20181013%2F20181013154351_bc8a0150d1efc43e36eb8bb84817cc88_1.jpeg&fromurl=ippr_z2C%24qAzdH3FAzdH3F4z_z%26e3B45r_z%26e3Bv54AzdH3FwAzdH3F8b8a8n8c9nc89an_z%26e3Bip4s&gsm=0&rpstart=0&rpnum=0&islist=&querylist=&force=undefined" width="200"><img src="https://image.baidu.com/search/detail?ct=503316480&z=undefined&tn=baiduimagedetail&ipn=d&word=gakki&step_word=&ie=utf-8&in=&cl=2&lm=-1&st=undefined&hd=undefined&latest=undefined&copyright=undefined&cs=2348781574,1710157032&os=4264247687,2502332473&simid=0,0&pn=11&rn=1&di=8214782840&ln=1862&fr=&fmq=1549686406169_R&fm=&ic=undefined&s=undefined&se=&sme=&tab=0&width=undefined&height=undefined&face=undefined&is=0,0&istype=0&ist=&jit=&bdtype=0&spn=0&pi=0&gsm=0&objurl=http%3A%2F%2Fi0.hdslb.com%2Fbfs%2Farchive%2Feda3be62be0fc05a648c1d339c6d68dfc1153f8c.jpg&rpstart=0&rpnum=0&adpicid=0&force=undefined&ctd=1549686543798^3_1349X657%1" width="200"></center>]]></content>
      
      
